<p><strong>定义 1.3（Pareto 最优解）</strong>  若 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∄</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Ω</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\nexists \mathbf{x} \in \Omega</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.728em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord amsrm">∄</span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Ω</span></span></span></span> 使得 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>≺</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{x} \prec \mathbf{x}^*</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≺</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6887em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.6887em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mbin mtight">∗</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，则称 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{x}^*</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6887em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.6887em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mbin mtight">∗</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 为 <strong>Pareto 最优解</strong>。</p>
<p>Pareto 最优解集合定义为：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="script">P</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">{</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Ω</mi><mtext> </mtext><mo fence="true" lspace="0.05em" rspace="0.05em">|</mo><mtext> </mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">∄</mi><mtext> </mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Ω</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo>≺</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo fence="true">}</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{P}^* = \left\{ \mathbf{x} \in \Omega \,\middle|\, \nexists\, \mathbf{x}&#x27; \in \Omega, \mathbf{x}&#x27; \prec \mathbf{x} \right\}.
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7387em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.08222em;">P</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7387em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mbin mtight">∗</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0519em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">{</span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord">Ω</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="delimcenter" style="top:0em;">∣</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord amsrm">∄</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8019em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord">Ω</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8019em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≺</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">}</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">.</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>定义 1.4（Pareto 前沿）</strong>  所有 Pareto 最优解在目标空间中的像构成的集合定义为 <strong>Pareto 前沿</strong>：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="script">F</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">{</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>∣</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="script">P</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo fence="true">}</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{F}^* = \left\{ \mathbf{f}(\mathbf{x}) \mid \mathbf{x} \in \mathcal{P}^* \right\}.
